headline.main: MADAGASCAR DRIVE IMPERILS ANTSIRABE; Vichy Reports New Landings by British at Southern Ports

lead_paragraph: VICHY, France, Sept. 30 (AP) -- The French announced tonight that the British column advancing into the south of Madagascar from Tananarive was nearing Antsirabe after having captured Ambatolampy and pushed on about thirty miles beyond.
abstract: Madagascar: Brit take Ambatolampy; near Antsirabe; Vichy repts new Brit landings, Tulear and Pt Dauphin; repts French forces reorganized south of Tananarive and inflicting losses on Brit
